# Only local-only config is excluded from the deploy. Everything the app + site
# need at runtime is served: index.html, api/*.js, the PNGs, backtester/results.json
# (Backtester tab + Futures edge card fetch it), and the trader/ STRATA Live app
# (reachable at /trader/app/ — it uses the deployed /api/yf proxy + the root PNGs).
.claude
.gitignore
*.md
